    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>February 22<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> 5615</date>
            </p>
            <p>My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I beg to acknowledge<lb/> the receipt of your favor conveying
                the<lb/> resolution of the “Board of Managers” of<lb/> the Congregation over which
                you so<lb/> ably preside, in which I am honored<lb/> with the appointment “to
                perform the<lb/> Marriage Ceremony” for my Respected<lb/> friend and colleague the
                    <persName>Revd I Morais</persName><lb/> I need not say how much pleasure<lb/> it
                affords me to accept of this honor<lb/> and how sincere my wishes are for the<lb/>
                happiness of the Bride and Bridegroom<lb/> not only, but also for the continued<lb/>
                prosperity of your congregation, over<lb/> which, this important step on the<lb/>
                part of their worthy <add>חזן</add> can not fail<lb/> to exercise a most beneficial
                result.</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I shall take the earliest oppor<lb/>tunity to lay the invitation
                before my<lb/> Board of Trustees the result of which<lb/> I trust will be
                satisfactory and which<lb/> I shall take pleasure to communicate</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mrs Lyons</persName> joins with me in<lb/> kind regards to
                yourself and Lady<lb/> She intends, God willing to avail her<lb/>-self of this
                opportunity to visit<lb/>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> when she will personally<lb/> make her
                acknowledgments for your kind<lb/> remembrance of her wishes.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I remain with due respect</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">My Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">J I Lyons</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Abm Hart Esqr</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
